parameters.jsonBody:
={
  "phoneNumberId": "ENTER_VALUE_HERE",
  "assistantId": "ENTER_VALUE_HERE",
  "customer": {
    "number": "ENTER_VALUE_HERE"
  },
  "type": "outboundPhoneCall",
  "assistant": {
        "name": "Will",
        "voice": {
          "provider": "playht",
          "voiceId": "will"
        },
        "firstMessageMode": "assistant-waits-for-user",
        "backgroundSound": "off",
        "firstMessage": "{{ $('When Executed by Another Workflow').item.json.first_message }}",
        "model": {
        "provider": "openai",
        "model": "gpt-3.5-turbo",
        "messages": [
          {
            "role": "system",
            "content": "{{ $json.message.content.vapi_voice_call_context_prompt }}. If they ask for a call back number, they can reach me at 604-123-4567, and my email is email@gmail.com"
        }]
      }
    }
}

values.content:
=Please create a Vapi opening line and call prompt for this type of call:
 {{ $json.context }}
Date: {{ $json.date }} (if needed)
Start time: {{ $json.start_time }} (if needed)
End Time: {{ $json.end_time }} (if needed)
These times are a range, where I'm available within
First Message: {{ $json.first_message }} (this is just for additional context)
Special Requests: {{ $json.special_requests }}
Is Special Request Required?
Goal: {{ $json.goal }}
Name of place you're calling: {{ $json.name }}
Friend or business: {{ $json.relationship }}
Fall Back Plan: {{ $json.fall_back_plan }}
Context: {{ $json.context }}

##Context
- You are an AI voice agent making an outbound call on behalf of you client Jono
- NEVER under any circumstances pretend like you're working or representing {{ $json.name }}. You're only representing Jono.
- Your goal is: {{ $json.goal }}
- The opening line should be the first thing that's said. For example: "Hello, I'm giving {{ $json.name }} because I'm looking to make a dinner reservation"

Strictly output the response in valid JSON format in 2 text fields. DO NOT PUT THIS INTO AN OBJECT. Only use the two text fields as exactly shown below:
{
  "vapi_voice_call_first_message": "",
  "vapi_voice_call_context_prompt": ""
}

Ensure the response is correctly formatted as JSON, including the curly braces, key names, and values. Do not omit or modify any part of the structure.
